      cues:['Colleague/staff requesting informal, unrecorded "off-the-record" prescribing \u2014 a professionalism issue; GMC: don\u2019t prescribe outside a proper assessment or without records.','Treat her as any patient \u2014 proper consultation, stewardship, full documentation; confidentiality via access-controlled records, NOT hidden care.','Explain kindly; offer a proper appointment and encourage registration with her own GP; be alert to stress/dependence (sleeping tablets/controlled drugs).']
